plist_data.NSCameraUsageDescription: Enable camera access to enhance your AI assistant experience. Use visual input for AI analysis, document scanning, and image-based AI tools. Camera access allows our AI assistants to provide more comprehensive and visual assistance.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneUsageDescription: Allow Zeally to use your microphone for voice interactions with AI assistants. Record voice notes, use voice commands, and enable speech-to-text features. Voice interaction makes communicating with AI assistants more natural and efficient.
plist_data.NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription: Grant Zeally access to your photo library to enable AI image analysis, document processing, and visual AI tools. Import images for AI-powered editing, analysis, and enhancement features that make your AI assistant experience more comprehensive.
plist_data.NSUserTrackingUsageDescription: Zeally uses tracking to personalize your AI assistant experience and improve our AI tools. We analyze usage patterns to optimize AI responses, enhance tool recommendations, and develop better AI features. Your privacy is protected and data won't be shared without consent, except when required by law.
